snippet.title: Ben C
snippet.description:
The official YouTube Channel of Ben C.
Ben C is a Dj/Producer in duo with the talented Musician/Producer Kalsx.
You will discover a lot of Mixes, Artists and Sounds on the Melodic Electronic Music.

Booking :
Marie@teoxaneproduction.com

Demo :
Studio@teoxaneproduction.com

For Demo, please, send a Soundcloud private link.
We receive many requests and we cannot answer to all of them, all our apologize for that.
We only reply to artists who interest us and who already have a small discography which respects the style of the channel and the label.

🔊 Playlist Spotify :
http://bit.ly/PlaylistMTH
To integrate the playlist, Submit your track on :
https://www.submithub.com/playlister/ben-c
